# GeoIFC Assets

GeoIFC Assets is a QGIS plugin for connecting GIS features with IFC models.

The MVP is:

* associate a GIS feature with an IFC file
* open the IFC in an embedded viewer
* select IFC elements
* inspect IFC properties
* select one or more IFC properties
* map them to GIS fields
* write selected values into GIS feature attributes
* log the main workflow with developer logs and user logs

Out of scope for the MVP:

* indicator engine
* batch processing
* PostGIS
* IFC georeferencing
* custom profiles
* print-based diagnostics in plugin code

Sector profiles are an evolution after the MVP.

